[30;1m83 | [0m[35m# There are a few important trade-offs here:[0m
[30;1m84 | [0m[35m#    1. Durability: Unflushed data may be lost if you are not using replication.[0m

[30;1m508 | [0m[35m    The sticky assignor serves two purposes. First, it guarantees an assignment that is as balanced [0m
